title: Transforms
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A //transform// is a named function that reshapes a token's value before substitution.  Pipe a transform onto a token with `|`:

|!Token                              |!Effect                                     |
|`{{title\|to-upper-case}}`          |`"Dune"` → `"DUNE"`                         |
|`{{genre\|split-commas}}`           |`"sci-fi, classic"` → `"sci-fi classic"`    |
|`{{created_at\|iso-to-date}}`       |`"2026-05-17T21:36:24Z"` → `"20260517213624000"` |

